Package game.Capability

  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    Buyables
    An enumerable class of constants which represent the capability to buy a certain item from a vending machine
    DinosaurType
    A class of enum constants representing the 3 species of dinosaurs as capabilities such that they can be applied to the generic Actor type to avoid downcasting
    GameEnvironment  
    Gender
    A class which assigns capabilities based on the gender of a dinosaur
    ItemCapable
    An enum class which gives buyable items their capability of being themselves
    State
    gives items or actors a state of acitvity or inactivity.
    Status
    A generic collection of enums which represents states in which objects and actors may be in.
    TerrainData
    Can be use when we need to find out information about a terrain object from outside of its class
